# proxies.txt — one proxy per line in the format:
# ip:port:username:password
#
# Example:
# 192.168.1.100:8080:myuser:mypassword
# 10.0.0.1:3128:proxyuser:proxypass
#
# Copy this file to proxies.txt and fill in your proxy details.
# proxies.txt is excluded from version control to protect credentials.
